title: The Essential Hannibal Collection
description:
Hannibal, developed for television by Bryan Fuller, in its entirety as of August 2014.
This mega-torrent includes
Season 1, almost all in 1080
Season 2, almost (if not all) in 1080
The Thomas Harris Hannibal Series (ebooks)
1) Red Dragon
2) Silence of the Lambs
3) Hannibal
4) Hannibal Rising

Enjoy Will Graham and his many furry friends!
(Viewer discretion advised...)
